			<p>
				Simone is a product designer who specializes in design
				prototyping for mobile and AR/VR. 
			</p>
			<p>
				She is currently leading the
				design of a subscription-based content platform, shaping creator
				experiences, subscriber engagement, and content discovery to
				optimize how users find and interact with monetized content.
			</p>
			<p>
				Outside of work, you'll find her either hiking the woods, or
				cooking in the kitchen.
			</p>
